channel.title: Helious - Bringing back 317 that's been ruined
channel.description:
[CENTER][IMG]http://img163.imageshack.us/img163/4926/helious.png[/img] [/CENTER] [size=5][b]Introduction[/b][/size] Helious is current most advanced project, everything which is going to be done is going to get properly coded without any bugs left behind. Helious is going to give every player what they want and what they need. [size=5][b]Features[/b][/size] Some of the current features include: [ul][li]Sea Troll Queen[/li] [li]Premium System[/li] [li]Dialogues[/li] [li]Teleports[/li] [li]Death Plateau[/li][/ul] [size=5][b]Quests[/b][/size] [size=3]Death Plateau[/size] [B]Start the quest by talking with Denulth which is located in Buthorpe:[/B] [IMG]http://img231.imageshack.us/img231/8956/namnlsh.png[/img] [B]If you're lost, find out what to do next:[/B] [IMG]http://img809.imageshack.us/img809/3913/31307510.png[/img] [size=5][b]Media[/b][/size] [B]Get familiar with our home area & meet new people:[/B] [IMG]http://i53.tinypic.com/2411fky.jpg[/img] [B]Teleport to different areas & discover new places:[/B] [IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/2ef74ec.jpg[/img] [B]Get your combat stats up and become one of the best:[/B] [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/2moc86o.jpg[/img] [B]Learn the basics at the Tutorial Island:[/B] [IMG]http://img100.imageshack.us/img100/7/namnlsyo.png[/img] [B]Get started & try to get items on your own:[/B] [IMG]http://img201.imageshack.us/img201/2507/namnlso.png[/img] [B]Get to your first training area & level up your skills:[/B] [IMG]http://img339.imageshack.us/img339/2872/namnlsru.png[/img] [B]Level upp your fishing skill & get your own food:[/B] [IMG]http://img690.imageshack.us/img690/5977/namnlssd.png[/img] [B]Defend yourself & fight againts the Sea Troll Queen:[/B] [IMG]http://img51.imageshack.us/img51/8835/namnlsqs.png[/img] [size=5][b]Signature[/b][/size] [img]http://img641.imageshack.us/img641/3315/91887416.png[/img]
[img]http://img641.imageshack.us/img641/3315/91887416.png[´/img]
[size=5][b]Feedback[/b][/size] Your feedback, comments, suggestions, constructive criticism, etc are all appreciated :). [B]More information & pictures coming soon. This is a project which is going to open in the future & please reply :).[/B]
